**Enhanced MetaWalletGen CLI** - Version 2.0 with comprehensive security features, enhanced user experience, and production-ready functionality.

This enhanced version includes:
- Advanced encryption and security features
- Comprehensive input validation
- Progress tracking and enhanced user feedback
- Configuration management and environment variable support
- Enhanced logging and error handling
- Memory protection and secure data handling

All enhancements maintain the same MIT license while significantly improving security, usability, and functionality.
